    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "在世界的尽头有片神秘海域，只有自由不羁的灵魂才可到达，世人称之为&quot;不可知之地&quot;。据传，那里有72座心岛。由强大自由的岛主守护和建设；据传那里有一片灵魂之海，玩家与玩家将打破时空的边界，兴趣相投，灵魂共鸣，相互依赖，温暖彼此。<br>这里是一个拥抱自由和温暖的世界，玩家将作为岛主，可以随心所欲建设自己美轮美奂的岛屿；也可以与远道而的灵魂成为好友，安抚他们仿徨的心灵，为他们建设新的家园；也可以以其他玩家一起成为好友，一切建设您的小镇。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/3f52fa9f91a4e3059925546af5dd9be4.poster.avif?t=1672892775\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/3f52fa9f91a4e3059925546af5dd9be4.webm?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/3f52fa9f91a4e3059925546af5dd9be4.mp4?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>1.自由装扮和创造</strong><br>我们将提供10000平方米的可diy区域，游戏时间将于现实世界同步，在这里可以种植作物，收集资源，建设自己的城镇；还可以利用桥梁，坡道设计高地，河流，瀑布，营造一个美丽的花园世界。我们将提供提供多样的主题建筑及家具，无论意大利小镇，还是中国古典园林，或现代复古都市，都可随意设计。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/613aad9e183fc814810a4cb56817aee3.poster.avif?t=1672892775\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/613aad9e183fc814810a4cb56817aee3.webm?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/613aad9e183fc814810a4cb56817aee3.mp4?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2.多人联机共同探索</strong><br>我们是联网游戏，我们将允许玩家与玩家之间可一起在岛屿上开荒，耕地，建设；也可以一起潜水，飞翔，探索这个世界的秘密，发掘隐藏的宝藏。因此，我们游戏非常适合情侣或家庭成员一起玩哦。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/0b6a4ee1d90e1c4af88604930788a87c.poster.avif?t=1672892775\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/0b6a4ee1d90e1c4af88604930788a87c.webm?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/0b6a4ee1d90e1c4af88604930788a87c.mp4?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>3.与兴趣相投的陌生人邂逅</strong><br>我们将有一颗漂亮的“世界树”，玩家可通过“树洞”吐露自己的心情，并匹配与自己兴趣相投的陌生人，你们降跨越时空的阻隔，在游戏中建立联系，培养亲密度成为亲密伙伴。好友之间可以互换自己的稀有物产，并协助对方建设自己的岛屿。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/ca0d343b4da66e1a55eebb04af3b00dd.poster.avif?t=1672892775\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/ca0d343b4da66e1a55eebb04af3b00dd.webm?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214360/extras/ca0d343b4da66e1a55eebb04af3b00dd.mp4?t=1672892775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>4.丰富有趣的商业往来</strong><br>我们游戏中将内置一个复杂有趣的“期货市场”。玩家可像现实中一样，发挥自己的聪明才智，不断买入卖出，成为这个虚拟时间中最富有的玩家。我们在游戏内为他们颁发奖牌并奖励稀有的图纸和材料。",
